      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total stunner. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been meticulously cared for, garage-kept, and looks absolutely flawless inside and out. If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect 'like-new' ride without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty. Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
