    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a peerless example of the E46 chassis, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing. Engineered for the purist, it features a factory 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. This vehicle has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including professional subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the structural and internal integrity of the drivetrain. The suspension geometry is precise, and the atmospheric induction provides a linear power band that remains unrivaled. In showroom condition with a comprehensive service dossier, this M3 offers a visceral, analog driving experience with no deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
