    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands in showroom condition. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, and it shows. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple without any bolster wear, and the scent of factory-new materials persists. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium audio system, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a strict maintenance schedule exclusively at the dealership. I have a comprehensive binder of all service records, including the most recent multi-point inspection which returned a flawless report. This is a non-smoker, no-pet vehicle with zero accident history, offering the next owner the experience of a brand-new car at a pre-owned price point.",
      "price": 44900.0,
